The '''1949 Swiss Grand Prix''' was a [[Grand Prix motor racing|Grand Prix]] [[motor race]] which was held at [[Bremgarten Circuit|Bremgarten]] on 3 July 1949. The race was won by [[Alberto Ascari]] driving a [[Ferrari 125 F1|Ferrari 125]].<ref>http://www.statsf1.com/en/1949-hc/grand-prix-57.aspx</ref><ref>http://www.silhouet.com/motorsport/archive/f1/nc/1949/49ch.html</ref>
